N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 14 ยง 803.4 - Times and places for inspection of office records

State Regulations

Office records or copies thereof for which requests for
access have been approved may be inspected on business days at locations
specified by the records access officer between 9:00 a.m. and 4:30
p.m. Notes
